        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">

            <!-- Our Story -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Our Story</div>
                <div class="section-subtitle">Built on a Foundation of Thirty Years</div>
                <p>
                    Founded on the core principles of <strong>family, integrity, and technical mastery</strong>,
                    <strong>MYCASA Construction Services</strong> stands as the vital bridge between decades of
                    veteran experience and modern engineering precision.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our technical heritage was established in <strong>1996</strong> under the leadership of
                    <strong>Marcelo Chiong</strong>, Senior Technical Consultant and Electrical Engineer, who brings
                    <strong>30 years of field-proven expertise</strong> to every project we undertake. Today, MYCASA
                    is managed by a new generation of siblings — dedicated to upholding Mr. Chiong's legacy of quality
                    while meeting the advanced standards and expectations that modern clients demand.
                </p>
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    Under the direct technical guidance of Marcelo Chiong, we leverage three decades of specialized
                    experience in <strong>Technical Project Supervision</strong>. Having led and coordinated multi-trade
                    teams for 30 years, Mr. Chiong ensures that every stage of work — from electrical systems to final
                    finishing — is executed exactly according to specifications, with the precision that defines our
                    reputation.
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Vision & Mission -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Vision</div>
                <p>
                    To be the Philippines' most trusted specialty contractor, recognized for transforming complex
                    technical specifications into flawless, reliable physical results.
                </p>

                <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 25px;">Mission</div>
                <p>
                    To deliver professional, fully licensed, and high-precision construction services through the
                    powerful synergy of family integrity and veteran technical oversight. We treat every technical
                    requirement as a personal promise made to our clients.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Core Values -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Core Values</div>
                <div class="values-grid">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <strong>Precision</strong>
                        <span>We follow technical specifications and standards to the letter — no shortcuts, no
                            compromises.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <strong>Integrity</strong>
                        <span>A family name you can trust, built and upheld since 1996.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <strong>Mentorship</strong>
                        <span>We pass down 30 years of hands-on mastery and knowledge to every project and every team
                            member.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <strong>Accountability</strong>
                        <span>Fully licensed, professionally managed, and always answerable for the quality of our
                            work.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Commitment -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">The MYCASA Commitment</div>
                <div class="section-subtitle">Bridging Generations</div>
                <p>
                    At MYCASA, we do not merely complete construction projects — <strong>we preserve and build upon a
                        legacy of excellence</strong>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Every project is personally overseen by Marcelo Chiong, ensuring that his 30 years of technical
                    know-how is directly applied on-site, while being carefully passed down to our next-generation
                    management team. This ensures that the high standards and rigorous specifications we established
                    in 1996 remain the foundation of every result we deliver today — combining time-tested expertise
                    with modern methods.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Core Services -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Our Core Services</div>
                <div class="section-subtitle">Expertise Directed by 30 Years of Site Management</div>
                <ul class="services-list">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Specialized Electrical Works</strong>
                        <span>Our primary specialty. From complete system overhauls to new installations, upgrades, and
                            maintenance — we ensure every connection and component meets or exceeds national safety and
                            quality standards.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Architectural Refinishing</strong>
                        <span>High-grade varnishing, professional repainting, and surface enhancement services designed
                            to restore, protect, and elevate the aesthetic and value of your property.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Surface & Masonry Restoration</strong>
                        <span>Precision re-tiling, structural resetting, and masonry repairs. We address structural
                            shifts, wear, and damage to restore stability, durability, and appearance.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Minor Structural Repairs & Maintenance</strong>
                        <span>Swift, effective solutions for building upkeep, structural reinforcement, and general
                            restoration works — keeping your space safe, functional, and well-maintained.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Experience & Heritage -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Experience & Heritage</div>
                <div class="section-subtitle">Three Decades of Project Mastery</div>
                <p>
                    While MYCASA represents a modern, forward-moving firm, our leadership and technical team have been
                    a constant, trusted presence in the construction industry for <strong>30 years</strong>. Since 1996,
                    under the technical direction of Marcelo Chiong, our work has been deeply rooted in serving
                    <strong>The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints</strong> — acting as a preferred contractor
                    for their facilities across the region.
                </p>
                <div class="experience-box">
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left;"><strong>Projects Successfully Delivered:</strong>
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Chapels and Meetinghouses</strong> — new construction, expansion, and full
                            interior/exterior renovation</li>
                        <li><strong>Seminary and Institute Buildings</strong> — structural upgrades, system
                            installations, and finishing works</li>
                        <li><strong>Administrative & Office Facilities</strong> — fit-outs, maintenance, and compliance
                            upgrades</li>
                        <li><strong>Auxiliary Properties & Groundworks</strong> — structural repairs, utility upgrades,
                            and long-term preservation</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Our long-standing partnership is built on understanding the unique requirements, standards, and
                    expectations that come with sacred and institutional spaces. We have developed deep expertise in
                    working within strict guidelines, preserving design integrity, and delivering work that reflects
                    respect, quality, and durability. Every project carries the same care and precision established in
                    our very first assignment for the Church in 1996 — a standard we bring to every client today.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Contact Section -->
